examples.en: Few companies have the clout to handle such large deals.

examples.en: He'll clout me around the head if he finds out what I've done.

examples.en: An official protest could carry considerable clout.

examples.en: He clouted 19 home runs last year.

examples.en: She clouted the boy across the face.
She gave the stubborn handle a solid clout to make it turn.
